   STREAMING AUDIO

   Microphone Listen to live streaming audio of the meeting currently in
   progress.
   (This link will only function during live audiocasts. Please be
   patient, as meetings do not always start at the scheduled time. If you
   hear a recorded message, try again in a few minutes, or let the message
   repeat for up to five minutes until the next meeting starts.)

   You can view the agenda of each meeting as you listen, by clicking on
   the link to the right of its listing below.
